Package schema2template.example.odf

package schema2template.example.odf
Examples for the generation of source and reference for the OpenDocument XML format.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    OdfHelper
    Three ODF examples in one: 1) Create an ODF Reference in HTMLl 2) Create Source Code 3) Create simple ODF Python source
    OdfModel
    Model for ODF specific enhancements.
    PathPrinter
    ODF example class to print the MSV expressions in between a PuzzlePiece parent element and a direct PuzzlePiece child element.
    SourceCodeBaseClass
    Encapsulates the name of the java base class
    SourceCodeModel
    Model for Java specific enhancements like common base classes for elements and Java valuetypes for valuetypes used in schema.
